  "texts": [
    "Data privacy and security are fundamentals of any technology related to digital health.",
    "In this case, the autonomy of the patients is crucial and technology developers must carefully consider their consent while using their data.",
    "Patients may not be willing to accept these technologies unless they are confident about the transparency of usage and the security of their sensitive health data.",
    "This is especially important for data used in drug discovery research, as it has the potential to be misused for criminal purposes such as bioterrorism.",
    "This is why regulatory agencies play a significant role in the safe clinical adoption of new technologies."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}